Rain, thunderstorms and flooding are expected to continue for the rest of the week as heavy rain wreak havoc in Gauteng. After the SA Weather Service issued a flood warning on Thursday, the floodgates opened in many parts of Johannesburg and Pretoria, causing traffic consternation and flash floods. On Friday morning, the SA Weather Service listed the following updates: Here is a look at some of the places throughout Gauteng affected by the flood:          